{"tid":868169,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港可塞人數　特首:1千萬　中聯辦:5千萬　準特首:1億　我:84億","createTime":"2018-10-19T09:14:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-19T09:59:03.000Z","uid":47714,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b04744f6f5e1963d55f008e512bd02673bf297aa","tid":868169,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T09:14:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.ftchinese.com/story/001012080\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ftchinese.com%2Fstory%2F001012080&d=JRs4lXgZO4ob0PKLWGHlNeargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=313dd2a3\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ftchinese.com/story/001012080</a><br />\n<br />\n2007年06月15日<br />\n<br />\n香港特首曾蔭權(Donald Tsang)認為，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港應增加40%以上的人口，使人口數量達到1000萬</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n人口數量略低於700萬的香港，已經是地球上人口最稠密的地方之一。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_7bfda70d0100qszx.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fblog.sina.com.cn%2Fs%2Fblog_7bfda70d0100qszx.html&d=JRs4lXgZO4ob0PKLWGHlNeargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=4afdf61b\" target=\"_blank\">http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_7bfda70d0100qszx.html</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：Paul Peng<br />\n<br />\n原載《信報》<br />\n<br />\n目前在中國境內，人口近億的廣東、四川、河南等人口大省始終在國家政治、經濟生活中佔有重要地位。香港搞&ldquo;一國兩制&rdquo;，要想在國家的政治、經濟運行中發揮更大作用，佔更大分量，從而為<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>香港這&ldquo;一制&rdquo;爭取到更大的利益，需要香港擁有更多的人口。假如香港有5000萬人口，那麼中央政府在制定涉及香港的政策時，一定會更加慎重，更加尊重港人的意願。</strong></span>我相信這個淺顯的道理大家都會明白。近一點的例子，為什麼香港總是比澳門重要，除了經濟等因素外，其實最重要的因素還是香港有700多萬人口，澳門只有50多萬人口。目前香港本土人士的生育意願這麼低，要維持現有的人口規模已然不易，唯有靠移民或內地孕婦來港生子了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/cc17162/statuses/110389382690779136\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcc17162%2Fstatuses%2F110389382690779136&d=JRs4lXgZO4ob0PKLWGHlNeargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=9f2c70d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/cc17162/statuses/110389382690779136</a><br />\n<br />\n信報星期五paul peng身份: 中聯辦宣傳文體部長彭健恆<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://plastichk.blogspot.com/2009/07/blog-post_22.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fplastichk.blogspot.com%2F2009%2F07%2Fblog-post_22.html&d=JRs4lXgZO4ob0PKLWGHlNeargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=6b0485e1\" target=\"_blank\">http://plastichk.blogspot.com/2009/07/blog-post_22.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news_topic/nt_content.asp?sid=1805&amp;nt=np\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews_topic%2Fnt_content.asp%3Fsid%3D1805%26nt%3Dnp&d=JRs4lXgZO4ob0PKLWGHlNeargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=3956aaca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews_topic%2Fnt_content.asp%3Fsid%3D1805%26nt%3Dnp&h=488fe8d1\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news_topic/nt_content.asp?sid=1805&amp;nt=np</a><br />\n<br />\n政務司司長唐英年接受本報專訪時，就描繪了一幅粵港融合的遠景。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>他認為，香港的出路，在於一國兩制《基本法》框架下的融合發展觀</strong></span>。朝粵港融合的目標前進，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>香港的巿場規模可以由現在七百萬人口擴展至一億人口</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20140226/large/26la2p01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20140226%2Flarge%2F26la2p01.jpg&h=3b6a8f6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1870750/org/2657037ae0fcf495b9102a45ccb764a3.jpg/3xq_NAu7Oo0JpKLM-TamErZEs1KIoIPA90n_7vdJ_-4?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1870750%2Forg%2F2657037ae0fcf495b9102a45ccb764a3.jpg%2F3xq_NAu7Oo0JpKLM-TamErZEs1KIoIPA90n_7vdJ_-4%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=0adb5617&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://album.udn.com/community/img/PSN_PHOTO/grace127/f_5845130_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Falbum.udn.com%2Fcommunity%2Fimg%2FPSN_PHOTO%2Fgrace127%2Ff_5845130_1.jpg&h=faa59e83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e0/Crowd_in_HK.JPG/800px-Crowd_in_HK.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2Fe%2Fe0%2FCrowd_in_HK.JPG%2F800px-Crowd_in_HK.JPG&h=fe76ed40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/sEvZ6Y\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FsEvZ6Y&h=a4bd51de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/FJ6hin\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FFJ6hin&h=c33d8d32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/adM3op\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FadM3op&h=7ef1bbd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/bYza7e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FbYza7e&h=1a92d03b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/bVrXzZ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FbVrXzZ&h=db03ae9a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c8f99c0314e4824d78af3e43efbc59e5c8e9e86d","tid":868169,"uid":29093,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T09:17:02.000Z","msg":"市場規模 1 億人口， 既係可以做1 億人既生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e5f164eb22de7f30f2c40a63b7204b88b2ce061","tid":868169,"uid":29093,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T09:18:31.000Z","msg":"做1 億人既生意， 唐唐唔係話人口有1 億<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f3934fbd9e969d9a336002c9eca5c781c4a2a96","tid":868169,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T09:21:04.000Z","msg":"100層式監倉 開發全部土地 放50億都得啦"},{"pid":"820eb886165c313efc5ba721be38dbe4f3cd53e8","tid":868169,"uid":62815,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"reply